snippet.title: Theatre Kid Reacts to Spiritbox (Courtney LaPlante) Epic Outfits!
snippet.description:
On this channel we Stan all amazing woman (not you Amber Heard). So today we highlight the amazing front women of Spiritbox, Courtney LaPlante! She is Beautiful, Talented and has a jaw that could cut glass. God knows it cuts through my heart 😍
I think it's fun to appreciate some of the cool outfits she has gotten to wear as well as wonder "Why is she wearing a trash bag" all in the same video.
I hope you guys enjoy this one and let me know who I should do next? Maybe a Man person?

I have so much fun on my Twitch and I would LOVE to see you guys there!
